---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "@data/constants";

const pageTitle = `About Us | ${SITE.title}`;
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <section class="py-6 sm:py-8 lg:py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xxl px-4 md:px-8">
      <h1
        class="block text-balance text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl lg:leading-tight text-teal-500 dark:text-teal-300 ml-10"
      >
        A Little About Us
      </h1>
      <p
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5"
      >
        At our core, we're builders who are passionate about creating platforms
        that genuinely transform how people work and succeed. There's something
        magical about watching a team's productivity soar when their
        infrastructure just works, or seeing a startup scale effortlessly
        because we built their foundation right.
      </p>
      <p
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5"
      >
        We pour our hearts into every solution because we know that behind every
        technical challenge is a human story—people with dreams, deadlines, and
        the determination to build something amazing. Your success isn't just
        our business; it's our passion.
      </p>

      <h2
        class="block text-balance text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl lg:leading-tight text-teal-500 dark:text-teal-300 ml-10 mt-8"
      >
        Our Mission
      </h2>
      <p
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5"
      >
        We exist to fuel your growth. Our mission is to transform your cloud
        infrastructure into a catalyst for success—building platforms that don't
        just support your business, but accelerate it. We're not just
        consultants; we're partners in your journey, dedicated to delivering the
        robust, scalable solutions that unlock your true potential.
      </p>
      <h2
        class="block text-balance text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl lg:leading-tight text-teal-500 dark:text-teal-300 ml-10 mt-12"
      >
        What Makes Us Different
      </h2>
      <ul
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5"
      >
        <li>
          <strong>Growth-Focused Partnership:</strong> We don't just build infrastructure—we
          architect your competitive advantage. Every platform we create is designed
          to scale with your ambitions and drive measurable business results.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Battle-Tested Expertise:</strong> From complex migrations to custom
          cloud-native solutions, we've solved the challenges that keep CTOs awake
          at night. Our deep technical experience means fewer surprises and faster
          time to value.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Innovation Through Collaboration:</strong> We leverage cutting-edge
          open-source technologies and industry best practices to deliver solutions
          that are both innovative and reliable. Your success drives our passion
          for continuous improvement.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2
        class="block text-balance text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl lg:leading-tight text-teal-500 dark:text-teal-300 ml-10 mt-12"
      >
        Our Services
      </h2>
      <p
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5 mb-4"
      >
        From streamlined cloud migrations to fully custom platform engineering
        solutions, we deliver the technical excellence that transforms how your
        business operates. Whether you're scaling rapidly or optimising for
        efficiency, we craft solutions that grow with you.
      </p>

      <h2
        class="block text-balance text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl lg:leading-tight text-teal-500 dark:text-teal-300 ml-10 mt-12"
      >
        Ready to Accelerate Your Success?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="ml-10 mt-3 text-pretty text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 lg:w-4/5 mb-4"
      >
        Your next breakthrough is waiting. Partner with us to transform your
        cloud journey from challenge to competitive advantage.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
